---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="BoBlog - Tentang Kami"
  description="Mengenai platform BoBlog, visi kami, dan teknologi di balik layarnya."
>
  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 preserve-3d">
    <!-- Hero Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-24 animate-fade-in perspective-1000">
      <div
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2 glass-depth rounded-full text-sm font-black text-accent mb-8 animate-float-slow"
        style="transform: translateZ(40px);"
      >
        ✨ Sejarah & Visi
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-8 leading-none tracking-tighter text-3d">
        Tentang <span
          class="bg-linear-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >BoBlog</span
        >
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl opacity-70 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Platform blogging modern yang dirancang untuk mempertemukan ide kreatif dengan teknologi
        performa tinggi.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- 3D Stacked Content Cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start perspective-1000">
      <!-- Left side: Story & Mission -->
      <div class="space-y-10 preserve-3d">
        <section
          class="glass-depth rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-14 transform hover:translate-Z(30px) transition-all duration-500 border border-base-content/5 relative group overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors"
          >
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-3d flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-5xl">🚀</span> Misi Kami
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 text-lg mb-6">
            BoBlog lahir dari keinginan untuk menciptakan ruang berbagi yang tidak hanya cepat
            secara teknis, tetapi juga indah secara visual. Kami berkomitmen untuk memberdayakan
            penulis dengan sistem yang intuitif.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 text-lg">
            Kami percaya bahwa setiap artikel layak mendapatkan panggung terbaik, didukung oleh
            standar SEO yang matang dan pengalaman membaca yang super fluid.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section
          class="glass-depth rounded-[3rem] p-10 md:p-14 transform hover:translate-Z(20px) transition-all duration-500 border border-base-content/5 relative group overflow-hidden"
          style="margin-left: 2rem;"
        >
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-secondary/20 transition-colors"
          >
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-3d flex items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-5xl">🎯</span> Target Kita
          </h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed opacity-90 text-lg">
            Menjadi platform rujukan utama bagi para pengembang, desainer, dan antusias teknologi di
            Indonesia untuk menuangkan pemikiran mereka secara profesional dan elegan.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side: Tech Stack Grid -->
      <div class="preserve-3d space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-10 text-center lg:text-left text-3d">
          Teknologi di Balik <span class="text-primary italic">Layar</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          {
            [
              {
                name: "Astro.js",
                icon: "🚀",
                desc: "Framework Modern 60fps",
                color: "from-orange-500",
              },
              { name: "React", icon: "⚛️", desc: "Komponen Interaktif", color: "from-blue-500" },
              {
                name: "Tailwind v4",
                icon: "🎨",
                desc: "Desain Sistem Pro",
                color: "from-cyan-500",
              },
              { name: "Neon DB", icon: "🐘", desc: "Serverless Postgres", color: "from-green-500" },
              { name: "Prisma", icon: "💎", desc: "ORM Type-Safe", color: "from-indigo-500" },
              {
                name: "Lucia Auth",
                icon: "🔒",
                desc: "Sistem Keamanan Solid",
                color: "from-red-500",
              },
            ].map((tech, i) => (
              <div
                class="glass-depth rounded-3xl p-6 group hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-500 preserve-3d border border-base-content/5"
                style={`transform: translateZ(${20 + i * 10}px);`}
              >
                <div
                  class={`w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-linear-to-br ${tech.color} to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-4 shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform`}
                >
                  {tech.icon}
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-black text-lg mb-1">{tech.name}</h3>
                <p class="text-xs opacity-60 font-medium">{tech.desc}</p>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <!-- Extra CTA Box -->
        <div
          class="glass-depth rounded-3xl p-8 mt-12 bg-linear-to-br from-primary/10 via-transparent to-accent/10 border border-primary/20 text-center animate-float-slow"
        >
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Siap untuk Memulai?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-6">Jelajahi karya-karya terbaik kami di halaman blog.</p>
          <a
            href="/blog"
            class="btn btn-primary btn-md rounded-full px-8 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30"
            >Mulai Membaca →</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Floating Background Decor -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none z-[-1]">
      <div
        class="absolute top-[30%] left-[50%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-[180px] animate-blob"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[130px] animate-blob"
        style="animation-delay: 5s;"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
